Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------op--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.49,0:00:06.58,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}確かな想いを伝えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.02,0:00:18.40,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}戻らない時間に溺れぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.79,0:00:22.14,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今を抱きしめよう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.29,0:00:29.02,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}その微笑みを行ったり来たり　そばにいたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:36.73,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この手を伸ばす　先には何が待ってるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.95,0:00:42.86,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}終わらない物語の向こう　飛び立て
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:47.67,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}本当の気持ちでたどり着く場所へと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.91,0:00:51.66,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の翼を広げて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.96,0:00:58.67,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}廻りゆくメッセージ　幸せは胸にあるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.75,0:01:02.27,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あと少しの勇気　涙も必要なの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.46,0:01:06.49,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}強くなれるチャンスかもね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.62,0:01:13.09,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}温もりのリフレイン　この大切をずっと守りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.18,0:01:16.86,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心を重ねてく　絆を感じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:20.76,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰も一人じゃないんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.02,0:01:29.82,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同じ空の下　確かな想いを伝えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.49,0:00:06.58,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这份真情实感　好想将它传递
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.02,0:00:18.40,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}为了不沉溺于一去不返的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.79,0:00:22.14,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}紧紧拥抱今天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.29,0:00:29.02,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}深陷于那微笑之中　好想相伴在你的左右
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:36.73,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伸出手　前方应该有什么正等待着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.95,0:00:42.86,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}朝着那未完结的故事　飞奔而去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:47.67,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}怀着一颗真诚的心向着那千难万险之地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.91,0:00:51.66,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}张开心灵的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.96,0:00:58.67,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}循环传递着一个讯息　幸福就存于这胸中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.75,0:01:02.27,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}接下来的少许勇气　尽管须以眼泪相佐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.46,0:01:06.49,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但这或许正是变强的契机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.62,0:01:13.09,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}温暖的迭句　想要永远将这份珍重守护
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.18,0:01:16.86,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}彼此心绪交织　感受着这其中的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:20.76,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以说没有人是孤身只影的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.02,0:01:29.82,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同一片蓝天下　好想将这份真情实感传递
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------ed--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.77,0:22:19.77,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の奥集めた　今日の光を持って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.42,0:22:28.56,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}飛び込んだ未知の先　何が待ってるのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.85,0:22:37.90,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}未来への共鳴　想い出に重ねれば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.10,0:22:46.94,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}勇気になる　強さになる　一人じゃないから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.13,0:22:49.25,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（聴かせて）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.34,0:22:57.87,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明日もきっと会えるね　本当の笑顔で行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.06,0:23:06.75,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夢見る夜明けを　一緒に迎えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.92,0:23:15.93,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無限の時間よりも　瞬間を駆け抜けよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.18,0:23:27.13,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}その夢の声いつか聴かせてね　信じてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.77,0:22:19.77,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}怀揣着内心深处收集好了的今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.42,0:22:28.56,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}跃入未知的前方　那里有什么正等待着我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.85,0:22:37.90,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若是与未来共鸣　不断忆起今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.10,0:22:46.94,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就会生出勇气　就能变得坚强　也就不再是独自一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.13,0:22:49.25,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（让你倾听）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.34,0:22:57.87,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明天也一定会与你相遇　我会带着真诚的笑容前去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.06,0:23:06.75,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好想和你一起迎接梦想中的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.92,0:23:15.93,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}与其坐拥这无限的时刻　倒不如追赶那绚烂的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.18,0:23:27.13,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}相信我　总有一天会让你倾听那梦中的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------正文--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.22,0:01:42.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.27,0:01:45.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  千秋啊  欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.31,0:01:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好  熊田老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.34,0:01:50.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便坐吧  正好找你有事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.95,0:01:53.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能先借下体温计吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.57,0:01:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.47,0:01:57.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎有些发烧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.58,0:01:59.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天嘛  天气又暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.08,0:02:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您还是那么随便的下结论
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.54,0:02:04.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个  我有话跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:07.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是关于千秋你们班主任田中老师的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:09.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我看看  我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.60,0:02:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,36度9  是不是该休息下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.04,0:02:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温度不高就算了  我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:21.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  看错了  是37度1啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.84,0:02:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准确点儿是37度1分9厘  休息5分钟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.82,0:02:31.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就稍微休息会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:34.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  田中老师怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.06,0:02:38.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了对了  田中老师挺优秀的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:43.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保健老师熊田刚好凑巧  目前正好没男朋友哦  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.04,0:02:45.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能这么告诉他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.19,0:02:47.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真够腹黑的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:50.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会考虑的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.43,0:02:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.79,0:02:54.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要柠檬汽水糖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.62,0:02:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  总觉得很可怕  免了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.66,0:03:01.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  我觉得有点累
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.13,0:03:05.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯  貌似没发烧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:10.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好  拿着  以防万一给你点儿药
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.28,0:03:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:11.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:16.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊  舒服多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  下午的课要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:19.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:22.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是柠檬汽水糖吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.83,0:03:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  不过是精神疲劳罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.52,0:03:27.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.55,0:03:30.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.20,0:03:32.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.86,0:03:33.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.62,0:03:36.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运动会麻烦你负责救护了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:41.26,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}第12碗  一口也吃不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:44.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  南同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:46.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.33,0:03:56.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.86,0:04:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.65,0:04:03.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.75,0:04:05.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近回来得很晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:08.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是在干什么可疑的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.09,0:04:12.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当上运动会的负责人  有不少事要忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.15,0:04:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:16.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道还能有别的什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.45,0:04:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  没劲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.22,0:04:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你负责什么呢  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负责救护
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.97,0:04:27.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过啊  为什么这个时候开运动会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:31.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的小学还真是奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.19,0:04:33.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我说干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.95,0:04:36.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运动会真令人期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.59,0:04:37.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.27,0:04:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想快点儿回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.31,0:04:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少动嘴多动手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.96,0:04:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是回去晚点儿嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.68,0:04:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:04:59.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用扔下我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为是谁害的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:05.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.51,0:05:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你讨厌他？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.95,0:05:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么问
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:19.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,态度太冷淡了吧  明明是邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:20.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家也不一起走…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因为偶然住在隔壁  就必须一起回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:28.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是这个意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.47,0:05:37.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预备  跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.58,0:05:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  感觉不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.43,0:05:45.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.26,0:05:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.98,0:05:49.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.47,0:05:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.74,0:06:00.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被夏奈叫来的  呐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在为运动会做特训
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.91,0:06:05.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  别歇着了  特训还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.04,0:06:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？还来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了  不经过努力又何来胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想在运动会这华丽的舞台上取得好成绩  就只有特训了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:18.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  教练
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:24.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  你要不要一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:29.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要陪你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你姐姐她们好像玩得很高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是犯傻罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.98,0:06:52.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:55.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:07:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说什么就快说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:01.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:05.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:10.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同学  是个有趣的运动会就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛突然说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就明天见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个拐弯抹角的家伙  搞不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:46.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  这些也能拜托你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:49.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好哦  交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨能停就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:13.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:16.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气预报说会放晴的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天听说  隔壁那家又要搬了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.40,0:08:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.84,0:08:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.15,0:08:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔壁  有些漫画我还没看过  现在去借
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:47.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁他们打包之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:49.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…明天再去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.86,0:09:03.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜  实在是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:06.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个多好的家伙呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得亲近起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:24.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  还有这么多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:26.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的都交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.24,0:09:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么惯着她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬木负责折纸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马负责把纸展开成花的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我负责绑线去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:41.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些我来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:43.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个人一起来很快就干完了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:45.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.61,0:09:48.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少动嘴多动手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:49.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.53,0:09:53.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  南同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:57.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊  虽然现在说晚了点儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:09:59.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们俩都姓「南」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.44,0:10:02.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我冬马就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是  叫我千秋就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:12.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.81,0:10:14.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋…同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:16.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.78,0:10:17.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:19.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是女生！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起  冬马同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这叫法也很不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.35,0:10:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预备  跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  快冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.26,0:10:53.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉～运动会加上隔壁邻居搬家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们家事还真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.33,0:10:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.57,0:10:59.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是春天嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.94,0:11:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得跟季节无关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.40,0:11:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实有个家伙什么季节都很兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.96,0:11:13.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香你也参加什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.58,0:11:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有家属也能参加的比赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.29,0:11:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道呢  我得问问千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:24.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是那么悠闲自在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.77,0:11:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:30.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  南春香要参加运动会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.61,0:11:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.14,0:11:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想千秋一定很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.78,0:11:37.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.93,0:11:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:42.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.65,0:11:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也得去参加社团活动了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.40,0:11:53.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于要到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.85,0:11:54.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:06.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.18,0:12:14.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.11,0:12:17.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～今天好丰盛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.85,0:12:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因为明天是运动会了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.93,0:12:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.78,0:12:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会去给你加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.97,0:12:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不用来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.23,0:12:31.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说傻话  在运动会上加油可是家人的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.22,0:12:33.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一家人聚在一起加油  运动会才热闹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.02,0:12:37.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.67,0:12:39.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:41.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一家人聚在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望明天能放晴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.84,0:13:15.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始举行运动会开幕式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.17,0:13:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开始了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.93,0:13:20.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午餐就交给我了  南春香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:35.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:40.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤冈…为什么你会？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.41,0:13:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被叫来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:44.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人叫你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.45,0:13:48.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不好嘛  和我们一起加油吧  藤冈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:49.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.73,0:13:51.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面是第五个比赛项目  
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.45,0:13:54.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年级学生的百米赛跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.61,0:13:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋她们要参加哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.15,0:14:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊  内田  吉野  让大家看看特训的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.22,0:14:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各就各位  预备…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.05,0:14:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们自己搞定  一群笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:43.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参加借物跑的五年级学生  请马上集合
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么带着夏奈跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.32,0:15:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那个  因为没别的合适人选了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:21.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是  为什么拉着藤冈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:23.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父…父亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.79,0:15:29.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤冈是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.48,0:15:33.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这实在够爆笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.48,0:15:36.27,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤冈是父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:37.41,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.79,0:15:38.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…是父亲？明明只有初二啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.22,0:15:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是各班代表参加的化装游行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:46.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们班的代表是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.53,0:15:47.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.78,0:15:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和穿女装的阿真好像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:58.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.04,0:16:02.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这里  上午的比赛项目全部结束
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.07,0:16:07.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去教室里吃午饭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:14.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人没有来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:15.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.38,0:16:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要一起吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.32,0:16:22.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:30.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  请用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:32.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明什么也没干  别第一个就下手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.73,0:16:38.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你加油也是很耗能量的啊  
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬木也别客气  吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:43.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:49.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬木？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.56,0:16:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是第一次跟这么多人一起吃便当
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.33,0:16:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多吃点儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:59.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点儿吃就没了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.05,0:17:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  下午有项目需要家属参加  你怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？有那样的项目吗  我怎么没听说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:15.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又没打算让你去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.27,0:17:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是让春香参加了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.91,0:17:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.71,0:17:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太狡猾了  我也想参加啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:24.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是参加过了吗  借物跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.62,0:17:26.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想参加别的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.63,0:17:28.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我再陪你参加一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:32.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何如何  没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.43,0:17:33.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.33,0:17:34.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.39,0:17:35.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和南同学…是什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:48.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我为今天而准备的…最强的手制意大利面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.65,0:17:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水温也必须达到最佳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.47,0:17:54.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要一份那不勒斯风味的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:55.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午的比赛马上就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.19,0:18:03.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请同学们各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.24,0:18:12.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.12,0:18:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.43,0:18:27.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.51,0:18:29.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是第二十七个比赛项目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.72,0:18:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年级学生与爸爸或妈妈的两人三脚赛跑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.84,0:18:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各就各位  预备…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.13,0:18:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那么紧张啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:48.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:36.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运动会到这里就正式闭幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.70,0:19:37.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有没有意式黑胡椒面了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.39,0:19:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:39.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意式香辣面还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.45,0:19:40.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.05,0:19:44.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一会再收拾不也行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.44,0:19:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别抱怨了  快点儿干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.89,0:19:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊…为什么冬木不待到最后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.59,0:19:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬木呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.39,0:19:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.39,0:19:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他今天转学了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.86,0:19:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没听说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.07,0:20:04.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说他硬是要参加上午的比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.04,0:20:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都来了就待到最后嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.79,0:20:15.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.13,0:20:28.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想说什么就直说啊  蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.72,0:20:38.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷  春天还没到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:40.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  大早上起来就那么多废话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷就是冷  怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.61,0:20:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说废话也不会暖和起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.96,0:20:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我回来做点热乎的东西当点心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.00,0:20:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天下午没课
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.45,0:20:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有春香没课太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.04,0:20:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  就算你这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.14,0:20:58.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定今天上完上午的课就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:00.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:03.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！别无视我！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.15,0:21:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  交换留学生已经决定了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:20.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我打算让南同学去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.25,0:21:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么都没跟我们说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.82,0:21:33.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有什么内情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.08,0:21:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送别会要办得盛大一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.52,0:21:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.43,0:21:45.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中生真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.76,0:21:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  来得正好  快进来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.47,0:21:54.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香她…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.96,0:21:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗…骗人的吧  我都没听说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.56,0:23:31.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家常的醋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.86,0:23:33.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实在洗衣服时也有大用处
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.80,0:23:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微倒入一点儿来代替柔顺剂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.65,0:23:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服就会变得很柔软
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.82,0:23:39.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不会留下醋味  可以放心使用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.41,0:23:41.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对防止面料退色也很有效
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.71,0:23:43.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因衣服质地不同也会有不适用的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.42,0:23:44.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请事先调查好哦
